metadata.name: Purple Sunset
metadata.description:
The fruity terpenes express notes of sweet, citrus, and even spice alongside floral berries. Purple Sunset offers a calming high that may help you wind down without feeling sleepy and completely lethargic.

• Total Cannabinoids: 25-30%
• CBD: 1-2%
• CBG: 1%
• Terpenes: Sweet and Spicy citrus with berries and floral.
• Effects:  She’s a hybrid that leans Indica for many.

Created from 2193 photos, 731 stacks of 3 images each.
